    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No One’s Hero</strong> 是一款以古代为背景的2D横向卷轴跑酷游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将扮演一名无名信使，肩负着传递重要信息的使命。历史会铭记英雄，却不会记住那些让胜利成为可能的人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的目标是在每个关卡中生存下来，克服致命的挑战，并在越来越危险的环境中完成这段旅程。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自动奔跑，玩家可控制 <strong>跳跃</strong> 与 <strong>滑行</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >依靠时机把握与反应速度躲避致命障碍和敌人</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3条生命系统</strong> —— 有些危险会损失一条生命，另一些则会立即结束游戏</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >受到伤害后会进入短暂的 <strong>眩晕状态</strong>，迫使玩家在压力下恢复</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312540/extras/28b543e606f8d6af28d4863d1e0b0c6f.poster.avif?t=1768972302\" width=1170 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312540/extras/28b543e606f8d6af28d4863d1e0b0c6f.webm?t=1768972302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312540/extras/28b543e606f8d6af28d4863d1e0b0c6f.mp4?t=1768972302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏结构：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>单人战役模式</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>13个手工制作的关卡</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >灵感源自古代风景与神话的场景</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >难度逐步提升</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312540/extras/47161caea4cec672142cde5c7d383672.poster.avif?t=1768972302\" width=1170 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312540/extras/47161caea4cec672142cde5c7d383672.webm?t=1768972302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4312540/extras/47161caea4cec672142cde5c7d383672.mp4?t=1768972302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>独特之处：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在著名神话背后展开的故事</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演一位普通、无名、被历史遗忘的信使</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快节奏、以技巧为核心的玩法，没有升级系统 —— 只考验玩家的操作水平</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>额外游戏模式：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成战役后将解锁 <strong>硬核模式</strong>，专为高水平玩家打造</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>音效与氛围：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >灵感源自古代的氛围音乐与音效设计</p></li></ul>",
